Package: PubMatrixR
Title: PubMed Pairwise Co-Occurrence Matrix Construction and Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Tyler", family = "Laird",
      email = "tylerscottlaird@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person(given = "Enrique", family = "Toledo",
      email = "enriquetoledo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1460-4708"))
  )
Author: Tyler Laird [aut],
    Enrique Toledo [aut, cre] (ORCID: <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1460-4708>)
Maintainer: Enrique Toledo <enriquetoledo@gmail.com>
Description: Queries NCBI Entrez E-utilities to count pairwise
    co-occurrences between two sets of terms in PubMed or PubMed Central.
    It returns a matrix-like data frame of publication counts and can export
    hyperlink-enabled results in CSV or ODS format. The package also provides
    heatmap helpers for exploratory visualization of overlap patterns.
Depends: R (>= 4.5.0)
